name: KUNDALINI - AWAKENING
description:
KUNDALINI is the life force hidden within each of us. The serpents represent the Kundalini force at the base of the spine, when awakened it travels throughout the spiritual body, balancing the energetic mechanisms and chakras.
Kundalini derives from a Sanskrit word that literally means "coiled up like a snake" or "one that has the shape of a serpent".
This Cosmic energy is concentrated within each being, and through your consciousness, it can be expanded.

This is the first of three pieces in the KUNDALINI collection.
